description:
Discover the transformative power of the living God and explore the resurrection and ascension of Christ Jesus. What is the nature of our God in contrast to earthly leaders who have come and gone? Learn how Jesus, alive and seated in Heaven, intimately knows and cares for each individual, longing to hear personal prayers and offering forgiveness for a meaningful connection to His everlasting Kingdom. Embrace the timeless truth that the Gospel of Jesus is the answer that continues to change lives.
